  ministry `Ministry of Jal Shaktri`
  department `Department of Water Resources, River Development and Ganga Rejuvenation`
  longTitle `An Act to provide for the establishment of a Board for the creation of a reservoir at Rajghat by construction, on behalf of the Governments of Madhya Pradesh and Uttar Pradesh, of a dam on the Betwa river at Rajghat and for the regulation of such reservoir.`
